Insider Activity


Individual




Patricia Q. Stonesifer



Ms. Patricia Q. Stonesifer is President & Chief Executive Officer at Martha's Table, Inc. and Independent Director at Amazon.com, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Miraval Holding LLC and Amazon.com, Inc.
Ms. Stonesifer was previously employed as Vice Chairman by Smithsonian Institution, Senior Advisor by Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation Trust, and Senior Vice President-Interactive Media Division by Microsoft Corp. She also served on the board at Viacom, Inc.



